sequenceDiagram
    participant Alice as Alice (Client)
    participant Server as Server (HTTPS)
    participant Bob as Bob (Client)
    
    Note over Alice,Bob: REGISTRATION PHASE
    
    Alice->>Alice: Generate RSA Key Pair
    Alice->>Alice: Save private key to disk
    Alice->>Server: POST /register<br/>{username, password, public_key}
    Server->>Server: Hash password with bcrypt
    Server->>Server: Store {username, password_hash, public_key}
    Server-->>Alice: 200 OK
    
    Bob->>Bob: Generate RSA Key Pair
    Bob->>Bob: Save private key to disk
    Bob->>Server: POST /register<br/>{username, password, public_key}
    Server->>Server: Hash password with bcrypt
    Server->>Server: Store {username, password_hash, public_key}
    Server-->>Bob: 200 OK